Big brother Naija 3 definitely has left over wahalas. Some hours ago, an insider from Big brother Naija 3 winner, Miracle’s camp went on social media to advise Nina.
It is quite clear to all, that the chemistry and relationship between Nina and Big brother Naija 3 winner Miracle who were romantic partners, isn’t as hot as it was back in the house.
While a lot of fans have had one or two things to say concerning who is at fault, this particular individual with the handle sexygold89 who claimed to have opened a new IG account to anonymously warn Nina , came out to tell Nina that Miracle and his family do not care about her. This insider also added that Nina’s friend Tricia isn’t to be trusted. Nina however thanked the insider and she liked the comment.